            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Could my right hon. Friend define a little further what he meant by "a little while" in replying to the question put to him by the Leader of the Opposition as to the date for a Debate? Everyone appreciates the right hon. Gentleman's position and no one wants to embarrass the Government, but on the other hand he will realise that great anxieties have been caused and that a Debate should take place at some time.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
